‚ÄúLexical <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG_DESC">organization</ENAMEX> of nouns and verbs in the
<ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">brain,‚Äù Alfonso Caramazza</ENAMEX> and <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Argye E. Hills</ENAMEX> reported
